But the proof of the total...

20:09.277 --> 20:17.026
bankruptcy of this book is the fact that it is disowned even by the comments.

20:17.086 --> 20:18.968
This is the other Eleni.

20:18.988 --> 20:19.649
The other Eleni.

20:19.709 --> 20:20.971
Nobody bought it.

20:20.991 --> 20:22.072
It's dead in Greece.

20:22.132 --> 20:22.893
Did it sell at all?

